# Kyaxa Library - Video Game Launcher

## Phase 1: Project Setup & Core Structure
- [ ] Initialize Electron + Vite + React + TypeScript project
- [ ] Configure Tailwind CSS v4 + ShadCN UI
- [ ] Set up SQLite database with all tables (games, screenshots, dlcs, tags, game_tags, collections, collection_games, extras)
- [ ] Create Electron main process (IPC handlers, window management)
- [ ] Create app shell with sidebar navigation

## Phase 2: Scanning & Library UI
- [ ] Implement folder scanning logic (main process)
- [ ] Build library grid UI (Steam Deck style cards, animations)
- [ ] Implement scroll and filtering
- [ ] Build hero cover section

## Phase 3: IGDB Integration
- [ ] Implement IGDB API authentication (Twitch OAuth)
- [ ] Game search and metadata fetching
- [ ] Cover and screenshot downloading/caching
- [ ] Auto-match scanned folders to IGDB games

## Phase 4: Game Page & Launcher
- [ ] Build game detail page (cover, description, Metacritic, gallery, DLCs)
- [ ] Implement executable selector (file dialog)
- [ ] Game launching (child process execution)
- [ ] Playtime tracking (process monitoring + SQLite persistence)

## Phase 5: Features
- [ ] Favorites system (toggle + filter view)
- [ ] Tags management (CRUD + filter)
- [ ] Collections (create, add games, view)
- [ ] Extras/Mods (associate files/folders, open)

## Phase 6: Search & Settings
- [ ] Search functionality (name, tags, collections)
- [ ] Settings page (scan folders, IGDB credentials, preferences)
- [ ] Auto-scan on startup
